  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Create a Classroom for 600 Burundi women</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project enhances gender equality by building a vocational classroom to support over 600 women in developing sewing skills.  This will not only offer increased employment opportunities for these women, but also lead to the production of reusable sanitary pads to be distributed free of charge to girls of school-going age:  49% of whom are believed to miss up to 5 school days a month due to periods.</narrative>
